Dart ColorBlind

Dart ColorBlind is a game that I plan to publish on Google Play. The aim of the game is to test for color blindness by playing darts. Demo Video = https://youtu.be/FO6vDWoeL7k Github = https://github.com/erenboran/DartColorBlind

Fish Stack

Fish Stack is a clone game I made using stacking mechanich. The ship sails on the sea and catches the fish

Build Skytower

Build Skytower is a Tower building game when the apartments stack on top of each other, you must try not to fall them. https://youtu.be/IVZRr0efuRI

CubeStacker

This is a Hyper-Casual Clone stacking game simple and direct gameplay. The purpose is to challenge to stack more blocks. Stacking movable blocks and cutting off excess blocks. https://github.com/erenboran/CubeStacker

ABOUT

I am a Game Designer and Developer with a deep love for video game development and a lifelong goal to create unique, enthralling, enjoyable experiences. Learning new technology and languages helps me reach that goal.

My childhood dream was to make my own games. I have made my own games and game servers for 10+ years. Now I am improve myself on Unreal Engine and Unity(VR,HyperCasual).
